column5: Does anybody know if there's a launch near the N-W corner of the lake? I know there's 1 in Footes Bay, but is there 1 up past Chown Rd? thx
there's a boat ramp off Clear Lake rd, right in front of Fraser Island...but this might be too north for you
Careful because the Clear Lake launch is a sand beach.
Thx guys. We were up on Wed and used Foots bay. We wanted to go to the Chown Rd area. The Clear lake one seemed to be further away.
